an class="mobile_label">Collection</span></a></li><li class="community_link"><a class="action_btn" href="https://johnsterspacegames.itch.io/baldis-fun-new-school-plus-ultimate#comments"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" width="18" height="18" aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_comment" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" version="1.1" stroke-linejoin="round" role="img"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z" /></svg>Comments</a></li><li class="devlog_link"><a class="action_btn" href="https://johnsterspacegames.itch.io/baldis-fun-new-school-plus-ultimate/devlog"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" width="18" height="18" aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_news" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" version="1.1" stroke-linejoin="round" role="img"><rect x="1" y="3" width="22" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="6" y1="8" x2="18" y2="8"></line><line x1="6" y1="12" x2="18" y2="12"></line><line x1="6" y1="16" x2="18" y2="16"></line></svg>Devlog</a></li></ul><script type="text/javascript">new I.GameUserTools('#user_tools')</script><div id="wrapper" class="main wrapper"><div id="inner_column" class="inner_column size_large family_work-sans"><div id="header" class="header has_image align_center"><img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzk2ODExNDAucG5n/original/xUOfwX.png" alt="Baldi&#039;s Fun New School Plus Ultimate Edition"/><h1 class="game_title" itemprop="name">Baldi&#039;s Fun New School Plus Ultimate Edition</h1></div><div id="view_html_game_1072534" class="view_html_game_page view_game_page page_widget base_widget direct_download ready"><div id="html_embed_7450742" class="html_embed_widget base_widget embed_wrapper"><div data-height="360" data-width="640" class="game_frame game_pending start_maximized" style="width: 640px; height: 360px"><div class="restore_wrapper"><button class="restore_btn button"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" width="24" height="24" aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_play" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" version="1.1" stroke-linejoin="round" role="img"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polygon points="10 8 16 12 10 16 10 8"></polygon></svg> Restore Ultimate BFNS Plus</button></div><div class="iframe_placeholder" data-iframe="&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://v6p9d9t4.ssl.hwcdn.net/html/8101042/index.html&quot; allowtransparency=&quot;true&quot; webkitallowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; mozallowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; msallowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; scrolling=&quot;no&quot; id=&quot;game_drop&quot; allow=&quot;autoplay; fullscreen *; geolocation; microphone; camera; midi; monetization; xr-spatial-tracking; gamepad; gyroscope; accelerometer; xr; cross-origin-isolated&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;"><button class="button load_iframe_btn"><svg viewbox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" width="24" height="24" aria-hidden class="svgicon icon_play" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" version="1.1" stroke-linejoin="round" role="img"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polygon points="10 8 16 12 10 16 10 8"></polygon></svg> Run Ultimate BFNS Plus</button></div></div></div><div class="columns"><div class="left_col column"><div class="formatted_description user_formatted"><h1>Welcome To Baldi&#x27;s Fun New School Plus Ultimate Edition!</h1>  <p>BFNS Plus Ultimate Edition is the ultimate version of Baldi&#x27;s Fun New School Plus which is currently under development. Compared to the <a href="https://johnsterspacegames.itch.io/baldis-fun-new-school-plus-classic" target="_blank">Classic Edition</a>, Ultimate Edition&nbsp;is planned to include a lot more content and features, like an <strong><em>upgradable minimap</em></strong> and <strong><em>inventory</em></strong>, a <strong><em>shop</em></strong>, <strong><em>missions</em></strong> that can be completed to earn rewards, <strong><em>story elements</em></strong>, <strong><em>cutscenes</em></strong>, and&nbsp;more!</p>  <h1>A Look At Some&nbsp;Game Modes</h1>  <p>In the 1.0 release of Ultimate Edition, a total of 12 different gamemodes are planned to be included. Some of those gamemodes are:</p>  <ul><li><em></em><strong><em>STORY MODE: Go On An Adventure To Recover All Of Jimmy&#x27;s Lost Notebooks!</em></strong></li><li><strong><em>FREE PLAY MODE: </em></strong><strong><em>Replay Floors You&#x27;ve Completed In Story Mode As Any Player You&#x27;ve Unlocked!</em></strong></li><li><em></em><strong><em>ULTIMATE MODE: Can You Get All 18 Notebooks In A Giant School And Win?</em></strong></li><li><em></em><strong><em>RANDOM MODE: A Random School Is Selected Each Time You Play!</em></strong></li><li><strong><em>MINIGAME MODE: Replay Minigames You&#x27;ve Unlocked In Story Mode.</em></strong></li><li><em><strong>MULTIPLAYER: Play With&nbsp;Other Students Online!</strong></em></li></ul>  <p>But not all of them will be available to play from the start of the game.&nbsp;Instead, you&#x27;ll need to reach certain points in Story Mode to unlock them, which is the main gamemode in Ultimate Edition.</p>  <h1>Floor Builder</h1>  <p>The Floor Builder&nbsp;is a part of the Floor Customizer gamemode, and it&#x27;s where you can create custom floors which you can then play in the Floor Player. You can try out an outdated demo of the <a href="https://johnsterspacegames.itch.io/bfns-plus-ultimate-level-editor-demo" target="_blank">level editor here</a>.</p>  <h1>Credits</h1>  <ul><li><strong><em>Basically Games</em></strong> - Created the Baldi&#x27;s Basics series.</li><li><strong><em>MichaelDoesGaming</em></strong> - Voiced Matt.</li><li><strong><em>LeSabriGames200</em></strong>&nbsp;- Created some textures for the Floor Customizer gamemode.</li><li><strong><em>Nicec00lkidd</em></strong>, <strong><em>saintza4</em></strong>&nbsp;- Composed some of the soundtracks for the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLS8PHdAJErT7si8cBtWlIdYNWBDaaInUJ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" referrerpolicy="origin">OST</a>.</li><li><strong><em>Porky Powers</em></strong> - Did some of the Baldi voice lines.</li><li><strong><em>GrandGames</em></strong> - Gave some suggestions and ideas.</li><li>And <strong><em>many others</em></strong> who have contributed or helped out with this&nbsp;project!</li></ul>  <h1>Links</h1>  <p>Links to content relating to Baldi&#x27;s Fun New School&nbsp;Plus Ultimate Edition can be visited below:  </p>  <ul><li><strong><em><a href="https://baldis-fun-new-school-series.fandom.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" referrerpolicy="origin">BFNS Series Wiki</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;</em></strong><strong><em>My <a href="https://twitter.com/JohnsterGames" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" referrerpolicy="origin">Twitter</a> &amp; <a href="https://mastodon.gamedev.place/@johnsterspacegames" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" referrerpolicy="origin">Mastodon</a> Accounts&nbsp;(This Is Where I Post&nbsp;Updates On The Development Of BFNS Plus Ultimate Edition&nbsp;Including Teasers)&nbsp;|&nbsp;</em></strong><strong><em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCoP1hHqMzaPewASYG3KJYnQ" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" referrerpolicy="origin">BFNS Plus YT&nbsp;Channel (Development Footage Is Posted Here)</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;</em></strong><strong><em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLURarhFDayNaNxxWsgSwVc977bsjQn1FK" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" referrerpolicy="origin">BFNS Series Gameplay Playlist</a>&nbsp;| <a href="https://johnsterspacegames.itch.io/bfns-plus-ultimate-level-editor-demo" target="_blank"></a><a href="https://sites.google.com/view/customlevelnetwork" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" referrerpolicy="origin">BFNS Plus UE&nbsp;Custom Level Network</a>&nbsp;| <a href="https://discord.gg/2rUFrg3b5k" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" referrerpolicy="origin">Official JSG Discord Server</a></em></strong></li></ul>  <p><em>The Classic Editio